{
 "name": "RPlog_Nexu_Hunting_-_Part_2",
 "title": "Nexu Hunting (Part 2)",
 "summary": "The hunt for the escaped Nexu continues through the maintenance corridors of OS Paladin as the pilot Raxis and Sergeant Tal'sin Secura's team clear room after room, wary of the air shafts and ducts. Meanwhile the great gray Nexu winds through the maze of tubes and tunnels, driven by predatory instinct toward what it senses as a mortal threat to its mate and cubs. As the team marks formations and reports cleared sections, the converging paths of hunters and hunted set the stage for a deadly encounter in the cramped confines of the station.",
